title: Bandicam v1.9.0.397
description:
Bandicam will help you carry out a video record with high compression ratio, while keeping the video quality closer to the original work, and provides performance far superior to other programs that provide similar functions.

Features:

-Bandicam can record DirectX/OpenGL programs like the Fraps
-The recorded file size is much smaller than other software
-You can upload the recorded file to YouTube without converting
-You can record over 24 hours without stopping
-You can record video at resolutions up to 2560x1600 in high quality
-You will experience much less lag than with other capture programs

Software website: http://www.bandicam.com
